OL,3,CVictoria Beckham says she and David
OL,4,C'always tried to be the best parents'
OL,6,FVictoria Beckham has said she and
OL,7,Fhusband David "always tried to be the
OL,8,Fbest parents that we can be" in her
OL,9,Ffirst interview since her son Brooklyn
OL,10,Fmade a series of allegations against
OL,11,Fhis parents.
OL,13,F"I think that we've always - we love
OL,14,Four children so much," she said in an
OL,15,Finterview with The Wall Street Journal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
