OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1776373859
OL,3,CVictoria Beckham says she and David
OL,4,C'always tried to be the best parents'
OL,6,F"We've always tried to be the best
OL,7,Fparents that we can be. And you know,
OL,8,Fwe've been in the public eye for more
OL,9,Fthan 30 years right now, and all we've
OL,10,Fever tried to do is protect our
OL,11,Fchildren and love our children.
OL,13,F"And you know, that's all I really
OL,14,Fwant to say about it."
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
