CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1776373859
OL,3,CVictoria Beckham says she and David
OL,4,C'always tried to be the best parents'
OL,6,FThe interview comes months after
OL,7,FBrooklyn accused his family of
OL,8,Fcontrolling behaviour, putting "brand
OL,9,FBeckham" before all else, and trying
OL,10,Fto "endlessly ruin" his relationship
OL,11,Fwith wife Nicola Peltz Beckham on
OL,12,Fseveral occasions.
OL,14,F"The performative social media posts,
OL,15,Ffamily events and inauthentic
OL,16,Frelationships have been a fixture of
OL,17,Fthe life I was born into," he wrote in
OL,18,Fa lengthy Instagram post in February.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
