PN,30904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1776373859
OL,3,CVictoria Beckham says she and David
OL,4,C'always tried to be the best parents'
OL,6,FThe only other public interaction
OL,7,Fbetween the two was the Beckhams
OL,8,Fwishing their son a happy birthday
OL,9,Flast month.
OL,11,FDavid shared two photographs, the
OL,12,Ffirst of himself, Victoria, and a
OL,13,Fyoung Brooklyn in a pool, with a
OL,14,Fcaption that said "27 today. Happy
OL,15,FBirthday Bust. We love you."
OL,17,FVictoria said the negative press has
OL,18,Fnot affected her business.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
