PN,30905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1776373859
OL,3,CVictoria Beckham says she and David
OL,4,C'always tried to be the best parents'
OL,6,F"I think that ultimately people are
OL,7,Fbuying my product because the product
OL,8,Fis really good. I don't think they're
OL,9,Fbuying my eyeliner just because it's
OL,10,Fme."
OL,12,FThe media attention may actually have
OL,13,Fearned her extra support, with her
OL,14,F2001 song Not Such an Innocent Girl
OL,15,Fhit number one on the iTunes chart
OL,16,Fafter a social media campaign by fans.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
