OL,3,CVictoria Beckham says she and David
OL,4,C'always tried to be the best parents'
OL,6,FThe campaign described the fact that
OL,7,FVictoria Beckham was the only former
OL,8,FSpice Girl not to have a number one
OL,9,Ffor her solo work as a "national
OL,10,Ftragedy".
